<h2>Welcome to HELDORYA</h2>
<p>Step into a thrilling modded Minecraft adventure, where magic, mystery, and medieval grandeur collide. Join our vibrant community on a Forge 1.20.1 server packed with carefully selected mods to enhance your experience. Whether you’re a builder, explorer, or warrior, HELDORYA invites you to shape your own destiny!</p>
</section>

<section id="explore">
<h2>Explore the World</h2>
<p>Discover vast lands teeming with new biomes, powerful mobs, and endless building possibilities. Our mods bring fresh content and challenges to every corner:</p>
<ul>
<li>Build your dream castle with enhanced blocks and tools</li>
<li>Explore mysterious new biomes with Biomes O’ Plenty</li>
<li>Confront legendary mobs from Alex’s Mobs and Dragon Mounts Legacy</li>
<li>Automate your world with Iron Furnaces and advanced storage solutions</li>
<li>Delve into deep caves and discover rare ores with Deeper and Darker</li>
<li>Customize your mounts and ride dragons across the skies</li>
</ul>
