<section id="laws">
<h2>Laws of the Land</h2>
<p>To keep the realm peaceful and fair, all travelers must observe these laws:</p>
<ul>
<li>Respect fellow players and staff. No harassment or discrimination.</li>
<li>Use appropriate language; keep chat friendly and medieval-themed.</li>
<li>Do not exploit glitches or use unauthorized mods.</li>
<li>Griefing and stealing are strictly forbidden and punished.</li>
<li>Report suspicious behavior or bugs to the admins promptly.</li>
<li>Follow all directions given by moderators and server rules.</li>
</ul>
</section>

